{"tid":2399020,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[數據分析]其實異世界轉生系係日本政府既陰謀","createTime":"2021-02-07T18:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T11:51:17.000Z","uid":8307,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9563430a6f11f35beba3eb84c4308a0342b0c40a","tid":2399020,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T18:39:27.000Z","msg":"細佬我每套異世界類動漫輕小說都會睇幾集<br />\n我粗略估計都大概睇左500套左右<br />\n當中有九成都係死亡後轉生,剩低0.9成就係無啦啦穿越,最後0.1成就係其他<br />\n<br />\n係死亡轉生去異世界類型<br />\n有百分之九十九都係救人而死,自殺只佔極少數<br />\n而大部份都係被車撞死<br />\n車既類型九成九都係大貨車<br />\n日本出口最多貨車,周街都係ISUZU,HINO,FUSO<br />\n<br />\n而主角既背景<br />\n超越七成都係宅男/啃老族<br />\n<br />\n根據我睇左多年神山健治版既攻殼機動隊<br />\n其實個情況同SAC SSS好似<br />\n就係一班廢老揸住舊錢等死,死左畢錢就流入返比政府<br />\n<br />\n所以綜合上述所講<br />\n異世界轉生其實係軟性洗腦<br />\n等啲低端人口快能啲死,將啲錢流返入政府到<br />\n同時可以利用班毒能走去拯救班高端人口既生命"},{"pid":"2d2c474bf8dcc470343095d98a78e7a27afa336f","tid":2399020,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T18:40:24.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n意識形態洗腦"},{"pid":"a5647a36899106b27a2b16556bcc26cd0d173dc0","tid":2399020,"uid":27864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T18:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://chomanga.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/f538c85945d05cd18d8fa0a2af5072e7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchomanga.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Ff538c85945d05cd18d8fa0a2af5072e7.png&h=7b5b65ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c56847b56798b6b60f1b8f61b2eedfa3512dbc7b","tid":2399020,"uid":36383,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T18:57:55.000Z","msg":"轉生卡車"},{"pid":"5103bd7fe4b925a68ba3edc2c89c9a9149aa6396","tid":2399020,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:10:18.000Z","msg":"高汁post留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd